# Get in touch

## Open a ticket

You can [open a ticket by filing an issue on our GitHub repository](https://github.com/PredictiveSingularity/DAOE/issues/new?template=Blank+issue). Please provide as much detail as possible, including the steps to reproduce the issue, the expected behavior, and any relevant screenshots or logs.

Just [make sure that there isn't already an issue opened for the same problem](https://github.com/PredictiveSingularity/DAOE/issues). If there is, you can add a comment to the existing issue instead of opening a new one.

## Chat with us

If you are just looking for a chat, you can also use our discussion space on GitHub [here](https://github.com/PredictiveSingularity/DAOE/discussions/). Keep in mind that every discussion is public and can be seen by anyone.
